<h2>Remebering Helps Healing</h2>
<p>A recent study out of Duke University states “one in every four Americans has no one to confide in”. We know that loneliness, isolation, and a lack of connection give way to depression and emotional stress which eventually takes its toll on our spiritual and physical well-being. Research has shown that social isolation and loneliness can impair the immune system. Through this community based art, deep personal connections are created and a diverse nurturing art as healing community is established.<p>
